fullplot: Younger brother Nick (Booboo Stewart), who has Asperger's syndrome, struggles to cope and understand after the death of his brother Chaz (Harry Shum Jr.). His parents are in denial about several things, and are not communicating or dealing well with the loss, but then Chaz's best friend, Randy, decides to become a mentor to Nick.
plot: Twilight's Booboo Stewart plays a neglected teen trying to make it through each day after tragedy strikes.
title: White Frog
